| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4566 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 41e5fc53-ce01-5b88-9760-1d8d43c289d6"
